@startuml
title Componentes internos de la API
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "Auth + Roles" as auth
component "Provenance Module" as provenance
component "Governance Module" as governance
component "Ingestion Module" as ingestion
component "Query Module" as query
component "Quality Module" as quality
component "Health Module" as health
component "Error + Validation" as cross
component "Observability" as obs
component "Database Module" as db

auth --> provenance
 auth --> governance
 auth --> ingestion
 auth --> query
 auth --> quality
cross --> provenance
cross --> governance
cross --> ingestion
cross --> query
cross --> quality
provenance --> db : writer/reader
 governance --> db : writer
 ingestion --> db : writer + transaction
 query --> db : reader
 quality --> db : writer/reader
 health --> db : readiness
provenance --> obs
governance --> obs
ingestion --> obs
query --> obs
quality --> obs
health --> obs

note bottom of ingestion
Registro y revisión coordinan
la transacción de negocio.
Repositories encapsulan persistencia.
end note

note bottom of query
SQL constante, parametrizado,
paginado y orientado a proyección.
end note
@enduml
